{"id":"FH-0490","name":"Invenção do Cobogó","type":"evento","subtype":"Urbanização","description":"O cobogó foi criado e patentiado em 1929, no Recife. Sua invenção foi um trabalho em conjunto de Amadeu Coimbra, português, Ernest Boeckmann, alemão e Antônio de Góes, Pernambucano. Leva nome a partir da junção dos 3 inventores Coimbra - Co Boeckmann - Bo Góes - Gó COBOGÓ","de":"The cobogó was created and patented in 1929, in Recife. Its invention was a joint effort by Amadeu Coimbra, a Portuguese man; Ernest Boeckmann, a German; and Antônio de Góes, a Pernambucan. Its name comes from combining the names of the 3 inventors: Coimbra - Co, Boeckmann - Bo, Góes - Gó, COBOGÓ.","period":"","reference_location":"","municipality":"Pernambuco","neighborhood":"","image":"https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gz9qOL4DCSgMRhfkMf15p4A98SXvkWTyXnCcTiRU_UeyawlQ4IzUz6gUqx0ZoqUnIxixVcZDP-UVe1I0PXztAJkiNOjOxQR01Z-whWUQZHBXd_aqPYm41x7QkDrtKRQck7mGv8DvamvfPXJ8FBTLok4fSBYGXxS3TtERTxMizDFhO7T9iXYJ_dauV6AlY2RA7n8n7YBMUAtdg?fife=s16383","aliases":[],"sources":[{"id":"FT-0001","title":"https://antonioaurel.github.io/data/projects/recife-history-connections/pages/sources.html","source_type":"url","author":"","year":"","url":"https://antonioaurel.github.io/data/projects/recife-history-connections/pages/sources.html","notes":""}],"edges":[{"target_id":"PE-AUS-0010","target_name":"Antônio de Góis","target_type":"personagem","type":"person","strength":1},{"target_id":"LC-0032","target_name":"Avenida Domingos Ferreira","target_type":"local","type":"local","strength":1},{"target_id":"FH-0493","target_name":"O Frevo","target_type":"evento","type":"historical_event","strength":1},{"target_id":"FH-0494","target_name":"O Maracatu","target_type":"evento","type":"historical_event","strength":1},{"target_id":"LC-0253","target_name":"Palácio do Campo das Princesas","target_type":"local","type":"local","strength":1},{"target_id":"FH-0305","target_name":"Revolução Praieira","target_type"